    # Download URL (optional)
    download: https://github.com/ultralytics/assets/releases/download/v0.0.0/cityscapes8.zip

## Link to this sectionUsage#

To train a YOLO26n-sem model on the Cityscapes8 dataset for 100 [epochs](https://www.ultralytics.com/glossary/epoch) with an image size of 1024, use the following examples. For a full list of training options, see the [YOLO Training documentation](/modes/train).

Train Example
    
    
    from ultralytics import YOLO
    
    # Load a pretrained YOLO26n-sem model
    model = YOLO("yolo26n-sem.pt")
    
    # Train the model on Cityscapes8
    results = model.train(data="cityscapes8.yaml", epochs=100, imgsz=1024)

